HOW WE PROTECT YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?
We have implemented security measures to ensure that your Personal Data is not lost, used or accessed without authorization, altered or disclosed. We restrict access to your Personal Data to those employees, representatives and other third parties who need to know your details. They will process your Personal Data in accordance with our instructions and will be subject to the confidentiality obligation.
We have put in place procedures to combat any alleged breach of Personal Data security and we will inform you and all authorities of the breaches that we are required to notify about.
HOW LONG WILL WE USE YOUR PERSONAL DATA?
We will only store your Personal Data to the extent required by the purposes of this Privacy Policy and to meet any legal, accounting or reporting requirements.
In order to determine the appropriate period of Personal Data storage, we will assess the amount, nature and sensitivity of Personal Data, the potential risk of harm resulting from the unauthorized use or disclosure of your Personal Data, the purposes for which we process your Personal Data, and whether we can achieve these objectives by other means and applicable legal requirements.
HOW TO CONTACT US?
You can contact us at any time with any of your Personal Data protection issues at: 
 
Tota Game LIMITED 
Email: totagamestudio@gmail.com 
 
We will respond to all your requests within the shortest possible time.